Titolo: Brave Frontier

Anno: 2013

Descrizione: Brave Frontier (ブレイブフロンティア, Bureibu Furontia) is a Japanese mobile role-playing game developed and published by A-Lim, originally for Apple's iOS and later for Android and Kindle Fire. It was first released in Japan by A-Lim on July 3, 2013, and later released worldwide by Gumi Asia on December 13, 2013. A sequel series titled Brave Frontier 2 was released only in Japan on February 22, 2018 while a Global-exclusive sequel, titled Brave Frontier: The Last Summoner is slated for release in Q3 2018.